<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='813816' id='t-813816'>but when there's a bug, and all programs have bugs,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='816499' id='t-816499'>you've got to de-bug it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='818208' id='t-818208'>You've got to go in, change it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='820198' id='t-820198'>and then re-execute,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='821820' id='t-821820'>and you iterate,</span>
