</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='829434' id='t-829434'>So that led to my own work with Seymour</span>
